Feature: Landing Page Navigation

  Scenario: Clear and Accessible Design
    Given a visitor accesses RocketNotes for the first time
    When they navigate through the Landing Page
    Then the page shows key elements like the navigation bar and information sections on features, pricing, and contact

  Scenario: Visual Feedback on Interaction
    Given a visitor interacts with the navigation bar or dropdown menus
    When they select an option
    Then they receive immediate visual feedback like color changes or underlining
